headline: Martin Marietta Materials Inc. (MLM) Unveils SOAR 2030 Strategic Plan
summary: Martin Marietta Materials Inc. (NYSE:MLM) is one of the best cement stocks to buy, according to analysts. On September 3, the company introduced SOAR 2030, an ambitious five-year strategy aimed at strengthening its leadership in the aggregates-focused building materials industry.
